#: .\sa_book.json
msgid "High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology"
msgid_plural "High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology"
msgstr[0] "高級商業與軍事密碼學"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology',
#. 'str_pl': 'High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology'}
#: .\sa_book.json
msgid ""
"An incredibly dense volume describing different advanced cryptographical "
"methods, their strenghts, and weaknesses. This text would probably be easier"
" to digest with an added decade in Computer Science Academia."
msgstr "一本極其厚重的書，描述了不同的高級密碼學方法、其優勢與弱點。若在計算機科學學術界多待十年，或許能更容易消化這本著作。"
